@{
    Layout = null;
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - MeeCon</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: white;
            color: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 30px;
            background: #1e1e1e;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #00aaff;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #cccccc;
        }

        .highlight {
            color: #00aaff;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p><span class="highlight">MeeCon</span> is an innovative platform designed to simplify communication and collaboration. Our mission is to provide seamless and efficient tools for individuals and businesses to connect, share ideas, and achieve their goals together.</p>
        <p>With MeeCon, you can enjoy a user-friendly interface, advanced features, and a secure environment to enhance productivity and teamwork. Whether you are managing a project, hosting a virtual meeting, or simply staying in touch with your community, MeeCon makes it easy and effective.</p>
        <p>Our team is dedicated to continuous improvement and innovation, ensuring that MeeCon remains at the forefront of modern communication technology.</p>
        <p>Join us and experience a smarter way to connect!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
